sequenceDiagram
    participant Issuer
    participant DALP as DALP Platform
    participant Chain as ADI Chain
    participant Investor

    Issuer->>DALP: Create deposit asset
    DALP->>DALP: Compliance check
    DALP->>Chain: Issue on-chain token
    Chain->>Investor: Token delivered
    DALP->>Chain: Accrue interest
    Investor->>DALP: Redeem request
    DALP->>DALP: Redemption compliance check
    DALP->>Chain: Burn token
    DALP->>Investor: Fiat settlement confirmed
